overview:
Dr. Tamara Maule & Associates is an eye care clinic in Boca Raton Florida. Their optometrists offer professional eye care services like glaucoma testing and ocular disease diagnosis and treatment.

This Boca Raton eye care optometry provides the following services:

  • Eye exams
  • Contact lens fittings
  • Glaucoma screening
  • Cataracts diagnosis and treatment
  • Macular degeneration diagnosis
  • Routine eye exams
  • Pediatric eye exams
  • LASIK and eye surgery consultation

The eye doctors at this clinic also provide prescriptions for eyeglasses and contact lenses. Their optical carries a big selection of contacts which include:

  • Toric contact lenses
  • Multifocal contacts
  • Bifocal Contacts
  • Gas permeable contact lenses
  • Daily disposable contact lenses
  • Rigid contact lenses

The optical also provides a selection of eyewear and clients can find designer frames from many brand name manufacturers including sunglasses. Their opticians fit lenses to almost any frame.

This optometry practice serves the Boca Raton Florida area and the nearby areas of: Boyton Beach, Delray Beach and Coral Springs Florida.
